    "body": "You mean the response of `eth_getTransactionByHash` should return a confirmation count?\n\nI don't think this is good idea since it can give a false sense of accuracy. The fundamental problem remains, if you call this methods 2 times the results may vary. The longer you wait the more (relative) accurate the confirmation count will be. \n",
